ootball)|Bruce Clark]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">95</span> Kendall Walls\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">96</span> Sheldon Andrus\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">99</span> Tony Elliot\n\n| style=\"width: 25px;\" |\n| style=\"font-size: 95%;\" valign=\"top\" |\n'''Linebackers'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">51</span> Larry McCoy\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">52</span> [[Marcus Marek]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">53</span> Keith Fourcade\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">54</span> [[Bill Roe (American football)|Bill Roe]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">55</span> [[Joe DeForest]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">56</span> Ron Weisenhofer\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">58</span> Scott Leach\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">59</span> Roland Myers\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">91</span> Ken Marchiol\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">98</span> Fuzzy Huddleston\n\n'''Defensive Backs'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">20</span> John Sutton\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">22</span> Derrick Taylor\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">24</span> [[Milton Mack]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">27</span> [[Antonio Gibson]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">28</span> [[Gene Atkins]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">29</span> [[Reggie Sutton]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">32</span> Darrel Toussaint\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">33</span> [[Junior Thurman]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">38</span> Mike Turner\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">40</span> Michael Adams\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">48</span> Greg Harding\n\n'''Special Teams'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">4</span> [[Mike Cofer (kicker)|Mike Cofer]] K\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier